            -122-6454&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&nbsp;Privacy Policy
        </p>
        <hr />
        <div style="text-align:left;">
            <p>
                &copy; JXTravels All rights reserved.
                <br />
                <br />
                <span class="btn"><i class="fa fa-facebook"></i></span>
                <span class="btn"><i class="fa fa-instagram"></i></span>
                <span class="btn"><i class="fa fa-twitter"></i></span>
            </p>
        </div>

    </footer>

</body>

</html>